com.seamless.ers.client.externalws.dto
Class ClientContext

java.lang.Object
  com.seamless.ers.client.externalws.dto.ClientContext

public class ClientContext
extends java.lang.Object

Context structure used to authenticate and authorize a specific client request. When storing/representing this on the client end, it is recommended to handle this using a single URL-like string in the following format: // (since this is the standardized format and will typically be used when communicating client access information) eg: "RESELLERID:SE1004/9900/2009" "TERMINALID:10004537//1234"

kent
